title: [Witch Way]
description: A thick, rusted iron pole set deep into the ground in the middle of the area supports the torn, poor quality material comprising the tent's walls, which periodically buckle and sway under the pressure of the breeze outside.  The room itself is strangely dark, perhaps under the effects of some enchantment.  Near a narrow opening in the fabric of one wall leading out stands a single thin torch with a pale blue flame, scarcely illuminating the contents of the shop.
